36#include "hx_locl.h"
37
38
39static int
40null_init(hx509_context context,
41 hx509_certs certs, void **data, int flags,
42 const char *residue, hx509_lock lock)
43{
44 *data = NULL;
45 return 0;
46}
47
48static int
49null_free(hx509_certs certs, void *data)
50{
51 assert(data == NULL);
52 return 0;
53}
54
55static int
56null_iter_start(hx509_context context,
57 hx509_certs certs, void *data, void **cursor)
58{
59 *cursor = NULL;
60 return 0;
61}
62
63static int
64null_iter(hx509_context context,
65 hx509_certs certs, void *data, void *iter, hx509_cert *cert)
66{
67 *cert = NULL;
68 return ENOENT;
69}
70
71static int
72null_iter_end(hx509_context context,
73 hx509_certs certs,
74 void *data,
75 void *cursor)
76{
77 assert(cursor == NULL);
78 return 0;
79}
80
81
82struct hx509_keyset_ops keyset_null = {
83 "NULL",
84 0,
85 null_init,
86 NULL,
87 null_free,
88 NULL,
89 NULL,
90 null_iter_start,
91 null_iter,
92 null_iter_end,
93 NULL,
94 NULL,
95 NULL
96};
97
98void
99_hx509_ks_null_register(hx509_context context)
100{
101 _hx509_ks_register(context, &keyset_null);
102}
